It’s that time of the week again — it’s time for another #MerchantMonday! Get to know one of South Pearl Street’s self-care merchants, Clean Your Dirty Face 🍌💖🫧 ( @cleanyourdirtyface )

Clean Your Dirty Face is dedicated to delivering top-notch skincare solutions, ensuring a radiant and revitalized complexion. They offer services such as extractions to remove black heads, pumpkin peels to re-texturize your skin, and hydra boosts to stimulate collagen reproduction.

Clean Your Dirty Face has been open on South Pearl Street for just over a year! If you haven’t visited before, you can get your first facial for just $35 with the code VIRGIN.
